+## list
+
+Lists saved records from the local vault.
+
+```text
+python pala.py list --limit 10
+```
+
+Useful filters:
+
+| Option | Purpose |
+|---|---|
+| `--all` | Explicitly scan every date folder |
+| `--date 2026-06-09` | Limit to one date folder |
+| `--source codex` | Limit by record source |
+| `--project trugurpala/pala-memory-core` | Limit by linked project |
+| `--tag mobile-share` | Require a tag |
+| `--json` | Print machine-readable output |
+
+## search
+
+Searches saved records by title, summary, source, tags, project refs, decisions, tasks, evidence, and Markdown raw text.
+
+```text
+python pala.py search "github backup"
+```
+
+Useful filters:
+
+| Option | Purpose |
+|---|---|
+| `--date 2026-06-09` | Limit search to one day |
+| `--source mobile` | Limit by source |
+| `--project trugurpala/pala-memory-core` | Limit by project |
+| `--tag smoke-test` | Require a tag |
+| `--metadata-only` | Skip Markdown raw text |
+| `--limit 5` | Limit visible results |
+| `--json` | Print machine-readable output |
+
+## show
+
+Shows one saved record by full id or id prefix.
+
+```text
+python pala.py show 20260609T131509Z
+```
+
+Print the Markdown/raw text body too:
+
+```text
+python pala.py show 20260609T131509Z --raw
+```
+
