@@ -0,0 +1,66 @@
+# v0.11 Recovery Search
+
+Date: 2026-06-09
+Phase: recovery search preview
+Status: PASS for CLI recovery search and dashboard export/search preview
+
+## Goal
+
+Make saved Pala Memory Core records easy to recover after the original chat, phone share, or browser page is no longer visible.
+
+## Added Behavior
+
+| Area | Change |
+|---|---|
+| CLI | Added `python pala.py list` |
+| CLI | Added `python pala.py search <query>` |
+| CLI | Added `python pala.py show <record-id-or-prefix>` |
+| Dashboard | Added client-side search input |
+| Dashboard export | Added `python pala.py dashboard export --all` |
+| Schema | Added `mobile` and `playwright` source values |
+
+## Commands
+
+```powershell
+python .\pala.py list --limit 3
+python .\pala.py search "mobile share" --limit 2
+python .\pala.py show 20260609T131509Z
+python .\pala.py dashboard export --all
+```
+
+## Smoke Test
+
+Executed in `C:\Users\Pala-Home-1\Desktop\Codex\pala-memory-core`:
+
+```powershell
+python -m py_compile .\pala.py
+python .\pala.py list --limit 3
+python .\pala.py search "mobile share" --limit 2
+python .\pala.py search "published repo" --metadata-only --json --limit 1
+python .\pala.py show 20260609T131509Z
+python .\pala.py dashboard export --all
+```
+
+Observed key output:
+
+```text
+records found=8 scope=all records
+search found=4 query='mobile share'
+dashboard data saved dashboard\records.json
+scope=all records=8
+```
+
+Local HTTP dashboard verification:
+
+```text
+status=200
+hasSearch=True
+scope=all
+records=8
+```
+
+Browser snapshot verification was attempted through the Browser/Playwright connector, but the local Chrome Playwright Extension was missing. HTTP and exported-data verification passed.
+
+## Release Posture
+
+This is a recovery/search preview. It does not yet provide SQLite full-text indexing, OCR, semantic embeddings, or direct search across cloud services. It does make the local vault practically recoverable through CLI and dashboard filters.
